         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">23/3/94 ¶ (Good Friday) ¶  ¶ By this week's post, noble friend, you will again receive algae from Encounter Bay, ¶  where most recently the splendid Miss Hussey has also discovered  ¶ Claudea elegans ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">94.03.23</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Jacob Agardh</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. Avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund, Sweden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">23/3/94</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">(Oster Freitag)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Durch diese Wochen Post, edler Freund, werden Sie wieder Algen von Encounter Bay erhalten, wo in jüngster Zeit die prächtige Miss Hussey </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">
                     <name key="Claudea%20elegans">Claudea elegans</name>
                  </hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> auch entdeckt hat, als neu für Süd Australien. Die arme junge Dame ist absolut taub; so dass Sie</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">sie.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> wenig Genuss vom geselligen Leben haben kann, und sich glücklicher fühlt in der Einsamkeit nach Algen und anderen Pflanzen zu suchen. Sie schreibt, dass ich dadurch in Ihr</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">ihr.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> ein Feuer erlodert have,</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">habe.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> welches in Ihrem</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn4" type="footnote" n="4">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">ihrem.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> ganzen Leben nicht erlöschen würde.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nach langer Intervalle hat auf mein besonderes Drängen denn auch Miss Brooks versprochen, nach mehr Algen in der Israelite-Bay zu spähen,</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">Mit Ehrerbietung der Ihre</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">23/3/94</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">(Good Friday)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>By this week's post, noble friend, you will again receive algae from Encounter Bay,<note xml:id="ftn5" type="footnote" n="5">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">SA.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note> where most recently the splendid Miss Hussey has also discovered <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <name key="Claudea%20elegans">Claudea elegans</name>
               </seg> as new for South Australia. The poor young lady is absolutely deaf; so that she can have little enjoyment from social life and feels happier in her isolation in searching for algae and other plants. She writes that I have kindled a fire in her through this that would not go out in her whole life.<note xml:id="ftn6" type="footnote" n="6">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">Letter not found.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>After a long interval at my particular prompting Miss Brooks has also promised to look out for more algae in Israelite Bay.<note xml:id="ftn7" type="footnote" n="7">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">WA.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">With respect your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Claudea%20elegans">Claudea elegans</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
